<h3>Student training program</h3>
<p>
External PhD students can apply to the <it>Student training program</it> that each sector has by contacting its coordinator. It is possible to obtain a scholarship.
</p>
<h3>Visiting student program</h3>
<p> It is possible for italian universities to setup a convention that allows the university to share students, research activities and resources with SISSA.
For example PhD students are allowed to do part of their thesis here.
You can download a draft of the convention that is possible to stipulate using the following link. <br>
<a href='files/All. - Convenzione Visiting Students_SISSA.docx' >Visiting students convention form</a>
</p>
